name: Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo
title: New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo
description:
The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo is crafted with a waterproof GORE-TEX fabric, and dressed in a steel grey colorway.

Designed from a mixture of suede and mesh, the sneaker uppers display a grey hue that drapes over the toe boxes, quarters, and overlays that attach to the heel and tongues. A white N logo is on both its medial and lateral sides, while "2002R" text branding resides on the heel and at the tongue, and a GORE-TEX signature logo is stitched onto the toe box. Merging all this with a densely N-ERGY cushioned midsole, the sneakers portray, finishing off its appearance.

The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo was released on August 12th, 2022, and retailed for $180.

name: Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe
title: New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe
description:
The New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe was released as part of the 2022 ‘Protection Pack' by New Balance. 

The New Balance 2002R sneakers come in an indigo mesh upper with a series of taupe suede overlays. The shoe has an unfinished aesthetic provided by the raw and tattered edges. For branding, the shoe has a white ‘N’ logo and a '2002R' logo along the side. The lightweight ABZORB midsole provides cushioning along with N-ergy technology for improved shock absorption in the heel.

The New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe was released on 26th October 2022 with its retail price set at $170.

title: Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo
description:
The Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is inspired by outdoor adventure and pays homage to the rugged terrain of the Pacific Northwest.

The Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is equipped with Nike's Air Max technology, which provides excellent cushioning and support to the wearer's feet. The outsole of the shoe is made of durable rubber, which provides excellent traction and grip on a variety of surfaces.

We think that the notable feature of the Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is its premium Natural Indigo leather upper. This form of leather is a type of vegetable-tanned leather that is produced using natural dyes extracted from indigo plants. It is known for its durability and resistance to water and other elements, making it an ideal material for outdoor shoes. The Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo was released on December 19th, 2019, and retailed at a list price of $140.

name: Indigo Haze (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze W is an addition to Nike's Dunk lineup of sneakers in women's sizing. 

The Indigo Haze Nike Dunk Low W has a low-cut silhouette that allows for easy movement of the foot, while the padded collar and tongue offer additional cushioning and support around the ankle. Additionally, the shoe features a rubber sole that provides grip and durability, making it suitable for a wide range of activities. The toe box is perforated for added ventilation while the Nike name branding is visible on the tongue and heel tag. The Nike Swoosh is on both sides in Indigo Haze.

We especially love the Low Nike Dunk in Indigo Haze for Women for its striking colorway. The sneaker has a Sail upper with contrasting Indigo Haze overlays and Coral Chalk accents which creates a sleek and stylish look. The Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze W was released on March 31st, 2023 at a retail price of $110.

name: White Natural Indigo Burgundy
title: New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy
description:
The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy comes in a white, natural indigo, and burgundy color scheme.

The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy has an upper constructed from leather with a deep indigo burgundy hue. The shoe features an EVA midsole for padding and comfort. The sneaker also has a cushioned tongue and collar. The shoe features a rubber outsole for grip and stability. The sneaker has a "new balance 550" lettering on the tongue and "NB'" branding on the heel. The shoe also features an "N" logo on the lateral sides and "550" lettering on one side. The shoe's midsole features "NB" and "new balance" lettering on it.

The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy was released at a retail price of $110 on October 19, 2022.

name: Vintage Indigo Beige
title: New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige
description:
The New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige is a retro-inspired sneaker that was released as part of the sports collection by the American brand.

This sneaker features a beige and white mesh and leather upper with hints of vintage indigo on the tongues, ankles, and branding. Other details include the trademark "N" logo on the sides, "550" labeling on the laterals, New Balance basketball branding on the tongue tag, midsole and heel, and a lace-up closing system. The design is finished with a white midsole that sits on an Indigo rubber outsole with a linear pattern.

The New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige made its debut on December 14th, 2022, retailing at $110.

name: Indigo
title: Jordan 12 Retro Indigo
description:
Ever since Michael Jordan’s memorable 1997 Flu Game, the Air Jordan 12s have been a pinnacle addition to the Jordan Brand lineage. In 2020, the Air Jordan 12 Indigo brings back everything that Jordan heads love about the sneaker.

The Air Jordan 12 Indigo shares a striking resemblance to 2012’s Obsidian retro. Most Jordan 12 retros feature tumbled leather, but the Air Jordan 12 Stone Blue takes on smooth grain leather. Hits of white on the toebox and midsole add contrast to a majority Stone Blue sneaker. From there, the iconic Jumpman logo is seen on both stamped on the outsole and embroidered on the tongue. These sneakers released in August of 2020 and retailed for $190.

name: Natural Indigo
title: New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo
description: The New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo is a stylish and comfortable sneaker that is perfect for everyday wear. Made with high-quality materials, this shoe features a natural indigo colorway that is both unique and eye-catching. The upper is constructed from premium suede and mesh, while the midsole is made from lightweight REVlite foam for superior cushioning and support. The outsole is made from durable rubber, providing excellent traction and grip on any surface. This sneaker was released on September 9th, 2022, with a retail price of $150. Whether you're hitting the streets or just running errands, the New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo is a must-have addition to your sneaker collection.

name: Indigo (Women's)
title: Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (Women's)
description:
The Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (W) is part of a Nike collection that pays homage to the Indigofera Tinctoria plant, commonly referred to as True Indigo. This women's sneaker features a white upper constructed using breathable canvas with synthetic suede overlays and an embroidered Indigo plant graphic. On its upper, it has a light blue swoosh and a light blue heel tab engraved with True Indigo’s scientific information. Furthermore, it boasts a white midsole and a rubber outsole.

The women's Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (W) was released on 15th June 2021. It retailed at $110.

name: Natural Indigo Suede
title: New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede
description:
The New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede is an iteration of the New Balance 550 in a Natural Indigo/Suede colorway. 

This low-top sneaker features an Indigo suede build with matching suede overlays and a White leather overlay on the ankle collar. A tonal ‘N’ logo with a Sea Salt outline appears on the sides,  with a contrasting ‘550’ branding on the lateral forefoot. Off White laces, tongue, and heel logo provide a contrasting tone to this colorway. A White chunky midsole with New Balance branding rests on a cream outsole. 

The New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede was made available on November 1st, 2022, retailing at $120.

name: Grey Indigo
title: New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo
description:
Inspired by 2000s runners, the New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo is an iteration of the New Balance 1906R  in a ‘Grey Indigo’ colorway.

The upper is made of a Natural Indigo mesh base with Castlerock leather overlays. Other upper details include the Navy Blue ‘N’ logo on the sides with a Silver outline, ‘1906’ branding on the lateral, tongue and heel branding, and a TPU heel counter. The sole unit features ABZORB and N-ergy cushioning and a Navy Blue rubber outsole with multidirectional treads for traction.

The New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo was released on August 12th, 2022, for a retail price of $155.

name: Moonbeam Natural Indigo
title: New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo
description:
The New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo reinvents the 1980s NB CT300 tennis shoe silhouette with an oversized cup outsole and side panel branding, a rubber toe wrap, and wavy lines all through the design.

  The upper of the New Balance Moonbeam Natural Indigo CT302 is moonbeam mesh with tonal overlays in suede and an indigo heel tab and the Heritage N court logo in smooth leather. Hits of team red appear on the insole and tongue, which sports exposed foam. The natural stacked ABZORB midsole matches the ProCourt-inspired leather tip wrap. The midsole is 1.7 mm higher in the heel, featuring miniature embossed branding. 

  Released on March 15, 2022, the New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo sold for $100 retail.

name: White Indigo
title: Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo
description:
The Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo features a white canvas upper with pale blue canvas Swoosh overlays and cork heel wraps. To match the moments of cork that are scattered throughout the design, a semi-translucent dubrae boasts a pattern reminiscent of it. At the heel, an embroidered flower design in a textbook illustration style. From there, a white and gum sole adds the finishing touch.

The Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo released in May of 2021 and retailed for $110.

name: Indigo
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LV8 Indigo
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 07 LV8 Indigo has become a celebrated addition with a White, Obsidian-white and Black color scheme.

Built with a white leather upper, this LV8 Air Force model by Nike is highlighted by an Aqua Blue tone on the canvas that runs through the Nike Swoosh logos to the heel tab. Special details include scientific facts about the plant christened on the heel tab and a True Indigo plant embroidered on the tongue. A White midsole that rests on a Dark Cider rubber outsole completes the design.

The Nike Air Force 1 07 LV8 Indigo was made available on April 29, 2021. Initially, it retailed at $110.

name: Indigo (GS)
title: Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS)
description:
The Air Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS) is a retro-inspired grade school release of the Air Jordan 12 sneaker in a two-tone Stone Blue/Legend Blue/Obsidian colorway.

The upper is constructed with stitched Stone Blue leather highlighted by a smooth leather mudguard dressed in white. Legend Blue is used on the branded heel pull tab, inner lining, and the Jumpman logo on the outsole tip. Other details include silver metal upper eyelets, ‘TWO3’ branding running down the tongue, and ‘23’ branding at the rear on the White midsole. The sole unit comprises a carbon fiber shank and a Stone Blue herringbone outsole.

The Air Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS) was released on August 22, 2020 for a retail price of $140.

name: Indigo (Women's)
title: Nike Air Force 1 Indigo (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Indigo W is a sneaker model that comes in a combination of obsidian, white, and black color scheme.

An indigo plant that is visibly embroidered both on the left shoe of this pair at the back left, as well as on the back right of the right shoe, is where the name of this sneaker came from. The white canvas overlays all around its toebox, the light-blue-colored Nike Swoosh overlay on its sides, as well as the second light-blue-colored brand mark on its heels, are all features of this Nike Air Force 1 for women.

The Nike Air Force 1 Indigo W made its debut on the 15th of May 2021 and it had a recommended retail price of $110.

name: Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo
title: New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo
description:
The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo is crafted with a waterproof GORE-TEX fabric, and dressed in a steel grey colorway.

Designed from a mixture of suede and mesh, the sneaker uppers display a grey hue that drapes over the toe boxes, quarters, and overlays that attach to the heel and tongues. A white N logo is on both its medial and lateral sides, while "2002R" text branding resides on the heel and at the tongue, and a GORE-TEX signature logo is stitched onto the toe box. Merging all this with a densely N-ERGY cushioned midsole, the sneakers portray, finishing off its appearance.

The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo was released on August 12th, 2022, and retailed for $180.

name: Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe
title: New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe
description:
The New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe was released as part of the 2022 ‘Protection Pack' by New Balance. 

The New Balance 2002R sneakers come in an indigo mesh upper with a series of taupe suede overlays. The shoe has an unfinished aesthetic provided by the raw and tattered edges. For branding, the shoe has a white ‘N’ logo and a '2002R' logo along the side. The lightweight ABZORB midsole provides cushioning along with N-ergy technology for improved shock absorption in the heel.

The New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe was released on 26th October 2022 with its retail price set at $170.

description:
The Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is inspired by outdoor adventure and pays homage to the rugged terrain of the Pacific Northwest.

The Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is equipped with Nike's Air Max technology, which provides excellent cushioning and support to the wearer's feet. The outsole of the shoe is made of durable rubber, which provides excellent traction and grip on a variety of surfaces.

We think that the notable feature of the Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is its premium Natural Indigo leather upper. This form of leather is a type of vegetable-tanned leather that is produced using natural dyes extracted from indigo plants. It is known for its durability and resistance to water and other elements, making it an ideal material for outdoor shoes. The Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo was released on December 19th, 2019, and retailed at a list price of $140.

name: Indigo Haze (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze W is an addition to Nike's Dunk lineup of sneakers in women's sizing. 

The Indigo Haze Nike Dunk Low W has a low-cut silhouette that allows for easy movement of the foot, while the padded collar and tongue offer additional cushioning and support around the ankle. Additionally, the shoe features a rubber sole that provides grip and durability, making it suitable for a wide range of activities. The toe box is perforated for added ventilation while the Nike name branding is visible on the tongue and heel tag. The Nike Swoosh is on both sides in Indigo Haze.

We especially love the Low Nike Dunk in Indigo Haze for Women for its striking colorway. The sneaker has a Sail upper with contrasting Indigo Haze overlays and Coral Chalk accents which creates a sleek and stylish look. The Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze W was released on March 31st, 2023 at a retail price of $110.

name: White Natural Indigo Burgundy
title: New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy
description:
The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy comes in a white, natural indigo, and burgundy color scheme.

The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy has an upper constructed from leather with a deep indigo burgundy hue. The shoe features an EVA midsole for padding and comfort. The sneaker also has a cushioned tongue and collar. The shoe features a rubber outsole for grip and stability. The sneaker has a "new balance 550" lettering on the tongue and "NB'" branding on the heel. The shoe also features an "N" logo on the lateral sides and "550" lettering on one side. The shoe's midsole features "NB" and "new balance" lettering on it.

The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy was released at a retail price of $110 on October 19, 2022.

name: Vintage Indigo Beige
title: New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige
description:
The New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige is a retro-inspired sneaker that was released as part of the sports collection by the American brand.

This sneaker features a beige and white mesh and leather upper with hints of vintage indigo on the tongues, ankles, and branding. Other details include the trademark "N" logo on the sides, "550" labeling on the laterals, New Balance basketball branding on the tongue tag, midsole and heel, and a lace-up closing system. The design is finished with a white midsole that sits on an Indigo rubber outsole with a linear pattern.

The New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige made its debut on December 14th, 2022, retailing at $110.

name: Indigo
title: Jordan 12 Retro Indigo
description:
Ever since Michael Jordan’s memorable 1997 Flu Game, the Air Jordan 12s have been a pinnacle addition to the Jordan Brand lineage. In 2020, the Air Jordan 12 Indigo brings back everything that Jordan heads love about the sneaker.

The Air Jordan 12 Indigo shares a striking resemblance to 2012’s Obsidian retro. Most Jordan 12 retros feature tumbled leather, but the Air Jordan 12 Stone Blue takes on smooth grain leather. Hits of white on the toebox and midsole add contrast to a majority Stone Blue sneaker. From there, the iconic Jumpman logo is seen on both stamped on the outsole and embroidered on the tongue. These sneakers released in August of 2020 and retailed for $190.

name: Natural Indigo
title: New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo
description: The New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo is a stylish and comfortable sneaker that is perfect for everyday wear. Made with high-quality materials, this shoe features a natural indigo colorway that is both unique and eye-catching. The upper is constructed from premium suede and mesh, while the midsole is made from lightweight REVlite foam for superior cushioning and support. The outsole is made from durable rubber, providing excellent traction and grip on any surface. This sneaker was released on September 9th, 2022, with a retail price of $150. Whether you're hitting the streets or just running errands, the New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo is a must-have addition to your sneaker collection.

name: Indigo (Women's)
title: Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (Women's)
description:
The Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (W) is part of a Nike collection that pays homage to the Indigofera Tinctoria plant, commonly referred to as True Indigo. This women's sneaker features a white upper constructed using breathable canvas with synthetic suede overlays and an embroidered Indigo plant graphic. On its upper, it has a light blue swoosh and a light blue heel tab engraved with True Indigo’s scientific information. Furthermore, it boasts a white midsole and a rubber outsole.

The women's Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (W) was released on 15th June 2021. It retailed at $110.

name: Natural Indigo Suede
title: New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede
description:
The New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede is an iteration of the New Balance 550 in a Natural Indigo/Suede colorway. 

This low-top sneaker features an Indigo suede build with matching suede overlays and a White leather overlay on the ankle collar. A tonal ‘N’ logo with a Sea Salt outline appears on the sides,  with a contrasting ‘550’ branding on the lateral forefoot. Off White laces, tongue, and heel logo provide a contrasting tone to this colorway. A White chunky midsole with New Balance branding rests on a cream outsole. 

The New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede was made available on November 1st, 2022, retailing at $120.

name: Grey Indigo
title: New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo
description:
Inspired by 2000s runners, the New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo is an iteration of the New Balance 1906R  in a ‘Grey Indigo’ colorway.

The upper is made of a Natural Indigo mesh base with Castlerock leather overlays. Other upper details include the Navy Blue ‘N’ logo on the sides with a Silver outline, ‘1906’ branding on the lateral, tongue and heel branding, and a TPU heel counter. The sole unit features ABZORB and N-ergy cushioning and a Navy Blue rubber outsole with multidirectional treads for traction.

The New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo was released on August 12th, 2022, for a retail price of $155.

name: Moonbeam Natural Indigo
title: New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo
description:
The New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo reinvents the 1980s NB CT300 tennis shoe silhouette with an oversized cup outsole and side panel branding, a rubber toe wrap, and wavy lines all through the design.

  The upper of the New Balance Moonbeam Natural Indigo CT302 is moonbeam mesh with tonal overlays in suede and an indigo heel tab and the Heritage N court logo in smooth leather. Hits of team red appear on the insole and tongue, which sports exposed foam. The natural stacked ABZORB midsole matches the ProCourt-inspired leather tip wrap. The midsole is 1.7 mm higher in the heel, featuring miniature embossed branding. 

  Released on March 15, 2022, the New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo sold for $100 retail.

name: White Indigo
title: Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo
description:
The Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo features a white canvas upper with pale blue canvas Swoosh overlays and cork heel wraps. To match the moments of cork that are scattered throughout the design, a semi-translucent dubrae boasts a pattern reminiscent of it. At the heel, an embroidered flower design in a textbook illustration style. From there, a white and gum sole adds the finishing touch.

The Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo released in May of 2021 and retailed for $110.

To shop all Nike Blazer shoes, click here.

name: Indigo
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LV8 Indigo
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 07 LV8 Indigo has become a celebrated addition with a White, Obsidian-white and Black color scheme.

Built with a white leather upper, this LV8 Air Force model by Nike is highlighted by an Aqua Blue tone on the canvas that runs through the Nike Swoosh logos to the heel tab. Special details include scientific facts about the plant christened on the heel tab and a True Indigo plant embroidered on the tongue. A White midsole that rests on a Dark Cider rubber outsole completes the design.

The Nike Air Force 1 07 LV8 Indigo was made available on April 29, 2021. Initially, it retailed at $110.

name: Indigo (GS)
title: Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS)
description:
The Air Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS) is a retro-inspired grade school release of the Air Jordan 12 sneaker in a two-tone Stone Blue/Legend Blue/Obsidian colorway.

The upper is constructed with stitched Stone Blue leather highlighted by a smooth leather mudguard dressed in white. Legend Blue is used on the branded heel pull tab, inner lining, and the Jumpman logo on the outsole tip. Other details include silver metal upper eyelets, ‘TWO3’ branding running down the tongue, and ‘23’ branding at the rear on the White midsole. The sole unit comprises a carbon fiber shank and a Stone Blue herringbone outsole.

The Air Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS) was released on August 22, 2020 for a retail price of $140.

name: Indigo (Women's)
title: Nike Air Force 1 Indigo (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Indigo W is a sneaker model that comes in a combination of obsidian, white, and black color scheme.

An indigo plant that is visibly embroidered both on the left shoe of this pair at the back left, as well as on the back right of the right shoe, is where the name of this sneaker came from. The white canvas overlays all around its toebox, the light-blue-colored Nike Swoosh overlay on its sides, as well as the second light-blue-colored brand mark on its heels, are all features of this Nike Air Force 1 for women.

The Nike Air Force 1 Indigo W made its debut on the 15th of May 2021 and it had a recommended retail price of $110.

name: Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo
title: New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo
description:
The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo is crafted with a waterproof GORE-TEX fabric, and dressed in a steel grey colorway.

Designed from a mixture of suede and mesh, the sneaker uppers display a grey hue that drapes over the toe boxes, quarters, and overlays that attach to the heel and tongues. A white N logo is on both its medial and lateral sides, while "2002R" text branding resides on the heel and at the tongue, and a GORE-TEX signature logo is stitched onto the toe box. Merging all this with a densely N-ERGY cushioned midsole, the sneakers portray, finishing off its appearance.

The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo was released on August 12th, 2022, and retailed for $180.

name: Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe
title: New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe
description:
The New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe was released as part of the 2022 ‘Protection Pack' by New Balance. 

The New Balance 2002R sneakers come in an indigo mesh upper with a series of taupe suede overlays. The shoe has an unfinished aesthetic provided by the raw and tattered edges. For branding, the shoe has a white ‘N’ logo and a '2002R' logo along the side. The lightweight ABZORB midsole provides cushioning along with N-ergy technology for improved shock absorption in the heel.

The New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe was released on 26th October 2022 with its retail price set at $170.

description:
The Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is inspired by outdoor adventure and pays homage to the rugged terrain of the Pacific Northwest.

The Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is equipped with Nike's Air Max technology, which provides excellent cushioning and support to the wearer's feet. The outsole of the shoe is made of durable rubber, which provides excellent traction and grip on a variety of surfaces.

We think that the notable feature of the Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is its premium Natural Indigo leather upper. This form of leather is a type of vegetable-tanned leather that is produced using natural dyes extracted from indigo plants. It is known for its durability and resistance to water and other elements, making it an ideal material for outdoor shoes. The Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo was released on December 19th, 2019, and retailed at a list price of $140.

name: Indigo Haze (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze W is an addition to Nike's Dunk lineup of sneakers in women's sizing. 

The Indigo Haze Nike Dunk Low W has a low-cut silhouette that allows for easy movement of the foot, while the padded collar and tongue offer additional cushioning and support around the ankle. Additionally, the shoe features a rubber sole that provides grip and durability, making it suitable for a wide range of activities. The toe box is perforated for added ventilation while the Nike name branding is visible on the tongue and heel tag. The Nike Swoosh is on both sides in Indigo Haze.

We especially love the Low Nike Dunk in Indigo Haze for Women for its striking colorway. The sneaker has a Sail upper with contrasting Indigo Haze overlays and Coral Chalk accents which creates a sleek and stylish look. The Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze W was released on March 31st, 2023 at a retail price of $110.

name: White Natural Indigo Burgundy
title: New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy
description:
The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy comes in a white, natural indigo, and burgundy color scheme.

The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy has an upper constructed from leather with a deep indigo burgundy hue. The shoe features an EVA midsole for padding and comfort. The sneaker also has a cushioned tongue and collar. The shoe features a rubber outsole for grip and stability. The sneaker has a "new balance 550" lettering on the tongue and "NB'" branding on the heel. The shoe also features an "N" logo on the lateral sides and "550" lettering on one side. The shoe's midsole features "NB" and "new balance" lettering on it.

The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy was released at a retail price of $110 on October 19, 2022.

name: Vintage Indigo Beige
title: New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige
description:
The New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige is a retro-inspired sneaker that was released as part of the sports collection by the American brand.

This sneaker features a beige and white mesh and leather upper with hints of vintage indigo on the tongues, ankles, and branding. Other details include the trademark "N" logo on the sides, "550" labeling on the laterals, New Balance basketball branding on the tongue tag, midsole and heel, and a lace-up closing system. The design is finished with a white midsole that sits on an Indigo rubber outsole with a linear pattern.

The New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige made its debut on December 14th, 2022, retailing at $110.

name: Indigo
title: Jordan 12 Retro Indigo
description:
Ever since Michael Jordan’s memorable 1997 Flu Game, the Air Jordan 12s have been a pinnacle addition to the Jordan Brand lineage. In 2020, the Air Jordan 12 Indigo brings back everything that Jordan heads love about the sneaker.

The Air Jordan 12 Indigo shares a striking resemblance to 2012’s Obsidian retro. Most Jordan 12 retros feature tumbled leather, but the Air Jordan 12 Stone Blue takes on smooth grain leather. Hits of white on the toebox and midsole add contrast to a majority Stone Blue sneaker. From there, the iconic Jumpman logo is seen on both stamped on the outsole and embroidered on the tongue. These sneakers released in August of 2020 and retailed for $190.

name: Natural Indigo
title: New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo
description: The New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo is a stylish and comfortable sneaker that is perfect for everyday wear. Made with high-quality materials, this shoe features a natural indigo colorway that is both unique and eye-catching. The upper is constructed from premium suede and mesh, while the midsole is made from lightweight REVlite foam for superior cushioning and support. The outsole is made from durable rubber, providing excellent traction and grip on any surface. This sneaker was released on September 9th, 2022, with a retail price of $150. Whether you're hitting the streets or just running errands, the New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo is a must-have addition to your sneaker collection.

name: Indigo (Women's)
title: Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (Women's)
description:
The Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (W) is part of a Nike collection that pays homage to the Indigofera Tinctoria plant, commonly referred to as True Indigo. This women's sneaker features a white upper constructed using breathable canvas with synthetic suede overlays and an embroidered Indigo plant graphic. On its upper, it has a light blue swoosh and a light blue heel tab engraved with True Indigo’s scientific information. Furthermore, it boasts a white midsole and a rubber outsole.

The women's Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (W) was released on 15th June 2021. It retailed at $110.

name: Natural Indigo Suede
title: New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede
description:
The New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede is an iteration of the New Balance 550 in a Natural Indigo/Suede colorway. 

This low-top sneaker features an Indigo suede build with matching suede overlays and a White leather overlay on the ankle collar. A tonal ‘N’ logo with a Sea Salt outline appears on the sides,  with a contrasting ‘550’ branding on the lateral forefoot. Off White laces, tongue, and heel logo provide a contrasting tone to this colorway. A White chunky midsole with New Balance branding rests on a cream outsole. 

The New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede was made available on November 1st, 2022, retailing at $120.

name: Grey Indigo
title: New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo
description:
Inspired by 2000s runners, the New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo is an iteration of the New Balance 1906R  in a ‘Grey Indigo’ colorway.

The upper is made of a Natural Indigo mesh base with Castlerock leather overlays. Other upper details include the Navy Blue ‘N’ logo on the sides with a Silver outline, ‘1906’ branding on the lateral, tongue and heel branding, and a TPU heel counter. The sole unit features ABZORB and N-ergy cushioning and a Navy Blue rubber outsole with multidirectional treads for traction.

The New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo was released on August 12th, 2022, for a retail price of $155.

name: Moonbeam Natural Indigo
title: New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo
description:
The New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo reinvents the 1980s NB CT300 tennis shoe silhouette with an oversized cup outsole and side panel branding, a rubber toe wrap, and wavy lines all through the design.

  The upper of the New Balance Moonbeam Natural Indigo CT302 is moonbeam mesh with tonal overlays in suede and an indigo heel tab and the Heritage N court logo in smooth leather. Hits of team red appear on the insole and tongue, which sports exposed foam. The natural stacked ABZORB midsole matches the ProCourt-inspired leather tip wrap. The midsole is 1.7 mm higher in the heel, featuring miniature embossed branding. 

  Released on March 15, 2022, the New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo sold for $100 retail.

name: White Indigo
title: Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo
description:
The Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo features a white canvas upper with pale blue canvas Swoosh overlays and cork heel wraps. To match the moments of cork that are scattered throughout the design, a semi-translucent dubrae boasts a pattern reminiscent of it. At the heel, an embroidered flower design in a textbook illustration style. From there, a white and gum sole adds the finishing touch.

The Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo released in May of 2021 and retailed for $110.

To shop all Nike Blazer shoes, click here.

name: Indigo
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LV8 Indigo
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 07 LV8 Indigo has become a celebrated addition with a White, Obsidian-white and Black color scheme.

Built with a white leather upper, this LV8 Air Force model by Nike is highlighted by an Aqua Blue tone on the canvas that runs through the Nike Swoosh logos to the heel tab. Special details include scientific facts about the plant christened on the heel tab and a True Indigo plant embroidered on the tongue. A White midsole that rests on a Dark Cider rubber outsole completes the design.

The Nike Air Force 1 07 LV8 Indigo was made available on April 29, 2021. Initially, it retailed at $110.

name: Indigo (GS)
title: Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS)
description:
The Air Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS) is a retro-inspired grade school release of the Air Jordan 12 sneaker in a two-tone Stone Blue/Legend Blue/Obsidian colorway.

The upper is constructed with stitched Stone Blue leather highlighted by a smooth leather mudguard dressed in white. Legend Blue is used on the branded heel pull tab, inner lining, and the Jumpman logo on the outsole tip. Other details include silver metal upper eyelets, ‘TWO3’ branding running down the tongue, and ‘23’ branding at the rear on the White midsole. The sole unit comprises a carbon fiber shank and a Stone Blue herringbone outsole.

The Air Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS) was released on August 22, 2020 for a retail price of $140.

name: Indigo (Women's)
title: Nike Air Force 1 Indigo (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Indigo W is a sneaker model that comes in a combination of obsidian, white, and black color scheme.

An indigo plant that is visibly embroidered both on the left shoe of this pair at the back left, as well as on the back right of the right shoe, is where the name of this sneaker came from. The white canvas overlays all around its toebox, the light-blue-colored Nike Swoosh overlay on its sides, as well as the second light-blue-colored brand mark on its heels, are all features of this Nike Air Force 1 for women.

The Nike Air Force 1 Indigo W made its debut on the 15th of May 2021 and it had a recommended retail price of $110.

name: Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo
title: New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo
description:
The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo is crafted with a waterproof GORE-TEX fabric, and dressed in a steel grey colorway.

Designed from a mixture of suede and mesh, the sneaker uppers display a grey hue that drapes over the toe boxes, quarters, and overlays that attach to the heel and tongues. A white N logo is on both its medial and lateral sides, while "2002R" text branding resides on the heel and at the tongue, and a GORE-TEX signature logo is stitched onto the toe box. Merging all this with a densely N-ERGY cushioned midsole, the sneakers portray, finishing off its appearance.

The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo was released on August 12th, 2022, and retailed for $180.

title: Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze W is an addition to Nike's Dunk lineup of sneakers in women's sizing. 

The Indigo Haze Nike Dunk Low W has a low-cut silhouette that allows for easy movement of the foot, while the padded collar and tongue offer additional cushioning and support around the ankle. Additionally, the shoe features a rubber sole that provides grip and durability, making it suitable for a wide range of activities. The toe box is perforated for added ventilation while the Nike name branding is visible on the tongue and heel tag. The Nike Swoosh is on both sides in Indigo Haze.

We especially love the Low Nike Dunk in Indigo Haze for Women for its striking colorway. The sneaker has a Sail upper with contrasting Indigo Haze overlays and Coral Chalk accents which creates a sleek and stylish look. The Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze W was released on March 31st, 2023 at a retail price of $110.

name: White Natural Indigo Burgundy
title: New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy
description:
The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy comes in a white, natural indigo, and burgundy color scheme.

The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy has an upper constructed from leather with a deep indigo burgundy hue. The shoe features an EVA midsole for padding and comfort. The sneaker also has a cushioned tongue and collar. The shoe features a rubber outsole for grip and stability. The sneaker has a "new balance 550" lettering on the tongue and "NB'" branding on the heel. The shoe also features an "N" logo on the lateral sides and "550" lettering on one side. The shoe's midsole features "NB" and "new balance" lettering on it.

The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy was released at a retail price of $110 on October 19, 2022.

name: Vintage Indigo Beige
title: New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige
description:
The New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige is a retro-inspired sneaker that was released as part of the sports collection by the American brand.

This sneaker features a beige and white mesh and leather upper with hints of vintage indigo on the tongues, ankles, and branding. Other details include the trademark "N" logo on the sides, "550" labeling on the laterals, New Balance basketball branding on the tongue tag, midsole and heel, and a lace-up closing system. The design is finished with a white midsole that sits on an Indigo rubber outsole with a linear pattern.

The New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige made its debut on December 14th, 2022, retailing at $110.

name: Indigo
title: Jordan 12 Retro Indigo
description:
Ever since Michael Jordan’s memorable 1997 Flu Game, the Air Jordan 12s have been a pinnacle addition to the Jordan Brand lineage. In 2020, the Air Jordan 12 Indigo brings back everything that Jordan heads love about the sneaker.

The Air Jordan 12 Indigo shares a striking resemblance to 2012’s Obsidian retro. Most Jordan 12 retros feature tumbled leather, but the Air Jordan 12 Stone Blue takes on smooth grain leather. Hits of white on the toebox and midsole add contrast to a majority Stone Blue sneaker. From there, the iconic Jumpman logo is seen on both stamped on the outsole and embroidered on the tongue. These sneakers released in August of 2020 and retailed for $190.

name: Indigo (Women's)
title: Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (Women's)
description:
The Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (W) is part of a Nike collection that pays homage to the Indigofera Tinctoria plant, commonly referred to as True Indigo. This women's sneaker features a white upper constructed using breathable canvas with synthetic suede overlays and an embroidered Indigo plant graphic. On its upper, it has a light blue swoosh and a light blue heel tab engraved with True Indigo’s scientific information. Furthermore, it boasts a white midsole and a rubber outsole.

The women's Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (W) was released on 15th June 2021. It retailed at $110.

name: Natural Indigo Suede
title: New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede
description:
The New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede is an iteration of the New Balance 550 in a Natural Indigo/Suede colorway. 

This low-top sneaker features an Indigo suede build with matching suede overlays and a White leather overlay on the ankle collar. A tonal ‘N’ logo with a Sea Salt outline appears on the sides,  with a contrasting ‘550’ branding on the lateral forefoot. Off White laces, tongue, and heel logo provide a contrasting tone to this colorway. A White chunky midsole with New Balance branding rests on a cream outsole. 

The New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede was made available on November 1st, 2022, retailing at $120.

name: Grey Indigo
title: New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo
description:
Inspired by 2000s runners, the New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo is an iteration of the New Balance 1906R  in a ‘Grey Indigo’ colorway.

The upper is made of a Natural Indigo mesh base with Castlerock leather overlays. Other upper details include the Navy Blue ‘N’ logo on the sides with a Silver outline, ‘1906’ branding on the lateral, tongue and heel branding, and a TPU heel counter. The sole unit features ABZORB and N-ergy cushioning and a Navy Blue rubber outsole with multidirectional treads for traction.

The New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo was released on August 12th, 2022, for a retail price of $155.

name: Moonbeam Natural Indigo
title: New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo
description:
The New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo reinvents the 1980s NB CT300 tennis shoe silhouette with an oversized cup outsole and side panel branding, a rubber toe wrap, and wavy lines all through the design.

  The upper of the New Balance Moonbeam Natural Indigo CT302 is moonbeam mesh with tonal overlays in suede and an indigo heel tab and the Heritage N court logo in smooth leather. Hits of team red appear on the insole and tongue, which sports exposed foam. The natural stacked ABZORB midsole matches the ProCourt-inspired leather tip wrap. The midsole is 1.7 mm higher in the heel, featuring miniature embossed branding. 

  Released on March 15, 2022, the New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo sold for $100 retail.

name: White Indigo
title: Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo
description:
The Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo features a white canvas upper with pale blue canvas Swoosh overlays and cork heel wraps. To match the moments of cork that are scattered throughout the design, a semi-translucent dubrae boasts a pattern reminiscent of it. At the heel, an embroidered flower design in a textbook illustration style. From there, a white and gum sole adds the finishing touch.

The Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo released in May of 2021 and retailed for $110.

To shop all Nike Blazer shoes, click here.

name: Indigo
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LV8 Indigo
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 07 LV8 Indigo has become a celebrated addition with a White, Obsidian-white and Black color scheme.

Built with a white leather upper, this LV8 Air Force model by Nike is highlighted by an Aqua Blue tone on the canvas that runs through the Nike Swoosh logos to the heel tab. Special details include scientific facts about the plant christened on the heel tab and a True Indigo plant embroidered on the tongue. A White midsole that rests on a Dark Cider rubber outsole completes the design.

The Nike Air Force 1 07 LV8 Indigo was made available on April 29, 2021. Initially, it retailed at $110.

name: Indigo (GS)
title: Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS)
description:
The Air Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS) is a retro-inspired grade school release of the Air Jordan 12 sneaker in a two-tone Stone Blue/Legend Blue/Obsidian colorway.

The upper is constructed with stitched Stone Blue leather highlighted by a smooth leather mudguard dressed in white. Legend Blue is used on the branded heel pull tab, inner lining, and the Jumpman logo on the outsole tip. Other details include silver metal upper eyelets, ‘TWO3’ branding running down the tongue, and ‘23’ branding at the rear on the White midsole. The sole unit comprises a carbon fiber shank and a Stone Blue herringbone outsole.

The Air Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS) was released on August 22, 2020 for a retail price of $140.

name: Indigo (Women's)
title: Nike Air Force 1 Indigo (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Indigo W is a sneaker model that comes in a combination of obsidian, white, and black color scheme.

An indigo plant that is visibly embroidered both on the left shoe of this pair at the back left, as well as on the back right of the right shoe, is where the name of this sneaker came from. The white canvas overlays all around its toebox, the light-blue-colored Nike Swoosh overlay on its sides, as well as the second light-blue-colored brand mark on its heels, are all features of this Nike Air Force 1 for women.

The Nike Air Force 1 Indigo W made its debut on the 15th of May 2021 and it had a recommended retail price of $110.

name: Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo
title: New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo
description:
The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo is crafted with a waterproof GORE-TEX fabric, and dressed in a steel grey colorway.

Designed from a mixture of suede and mesh, the sneaker uppers display a grey hue that drapes over the toe boxes, quarters, and overlays that attach to the heel and tongues. A white N logo is on both its medial and lateral sides, while "2002R" text branding resides on the heel and at the tongue, and a GORE-TEX signature logo is stitched onto the toe box. Merging all this with a densely N-ERGY cushioned midsole, the sneakers portray, finishing off its appearance.

The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo was released on August 12th, 2022, and retailed for $180.

name: Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe
title: New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe
description:
The New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe was released as part of the 2022 ‘Protection Pack' by New Balance. 

The New Balance 2002R sneakers come in an indigo mesh upper with a series of taupe suede overlays. The shoe has an unfinished aesthetic provided by the raw and tattered edges. For branding, the shoe has a white ‘N’ logo and a '2002R' logo along the side. The lightweight ABZORB midsole provides cushioning along with N-ergy technology for improved shock absorption in the heel.

The New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe was released on 26th October 2022 with its retail price set at $170.

name: Lahar Escape Natural Indigo
title: Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo
description:
The Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is inspired by outdoor adventure and pays homage to the rugged terrain of the Pacific Northwest.

The Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is equipped with Nike's Air Max technology, which provides excellent cushioning and support to the wearer's feet. The outsole of the shoe is made of durable rubber, which provides excellent traction and grip on a variety of surfaces.

We think that the notable feature of the Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is its premium Natural Indigo leather upper. This form of leather is a type of vegetable-tanned leather that is produced using natural dyes extracted from indigo plants. It is known for its durability and resistance to water and other elements, making it an ideal material for outdoor shoes. The Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo was released on December 19th, 2019, and retailed at a list price of $140.

name: Indigo Haze (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze W is an addition to Nike's Dunk lineup of sneakers in women's sizing. 

The Indigo Haze Nike Dunk Low W has a low-cut silhouette that allows for easy movement of the foot, while the padded collar and tongue offer additional cushioning and support around the ankle. Additionally, the shoe features a rubber sole that provides grip and durability, making it suitable for a wide range of activities. The toe box is perforated for added ventilation while the Nike name branding is visible on the tongue and heel tag. The Nike Swoosh is on both sides in Indigo Haze.

We especially love the Low Nike Dunk in Indigo Haze for Women for its striking colorway. The sneaker has a Sail upper with contrasting Indigo Haze overlays and Coral Chalk accents which creates a sleek and stylish look. The Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze W was released on March 31st, 2023 at a retail price of $110.

name: White Natural Indigo Burgundy
title: New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy
description:
The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy comes in a white, natural indigo, and burgundy color scheme.

The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy has an upper constructed from leather with a deep indigo burgundy hue. The shoe features an EVA midsole for padding and comfort. The sneaker also has a cushioned tongue and collar. The shoe features a rubber outsole for grip and stability. The sneaker has a "new balance 550" lettering on the tongue and "NB'" branding on the heel. The shoe also features an "N" logo on the lateral sides and "550" lettering on one side. The shoe's midsole features "NB" and "new balance" lettering on it.

The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy was released at a retail price of $110 on October 19, 2022.

name: Vintage Indigo Beige
title: New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige
description:
The New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige is a retro-inspired sneaker that was released as part of the sports collection by the American brand.

This sneaker features a beige and white mesh and leather upper with hints of vintage indigo on the tongues, ankles, and branding. Other details include the trademark "N" logo on the sides, "550" labeling on the laterals, New Balance basketball branding on the tongue tag, midsole and heel, and a lace-up closing system. The design is finished with a white midsole that sits on an Indigo rubber outsole with a linear pattern.

The New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige made its debut on December 14th, 2022, retailing at $110.

name: Indigo
title: Jordan 12 Retro Indigo
description:
Ever since Michael Jordan’s memorable 1997 Flu Game, the Air Jordan 12s have been a pinnacle addition to the Jordan Brand lineage. In 2020, the Air Jordan 12 Indigo brings back everything that Jordan heads love about the sneaker.

The Air Jordan 12 Indigo shares a striking resemblance to 2012’s Obsidian retro. Most Jordan 12 retros feature tumbled leather, but the Air Jordan 12 Stone Blue takes on smooth grain leather. Hits of white on the toebox and midsole add contrast to a majority Stone Blue sneaker. From there, the iconic Jumpman logo is seen on both stamped on the outsole and embroidered on the tongue. These sneakers released in August of 2020 and retailed for $190.

title: New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo
description: The New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo is a stylish and comfortable sneaker that is perfect for everyday wear. name: Indigo (Women's)
title: Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (Women's)
description:
The Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (W) is part of a Nike collection that pays homage to the Indigofera Tinctoria plant, commonly referred to as True Indigo. This women's sneaker features a white upper constructed using breathable canvas with synthetic suede overlays and an embroidered Indigo plant graphic. On its upper, it has a light blue swoosh and a light blue heel tab engraved with True Indigo’s scientific information. Furthermore, it boasts a white midsole and a rubber outsole.

The women's Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (W) was released on 15th June 2021. It retailed at $110.

name: Natural Indigo Suede
title: New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede
description:
The New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede is an iteration of the New Balance 550 in a Natural Indigo/Suede colorway. 

This low-top sneaker features an Indigo suede build with matching suede overlays and a White leather overlay on the ankle collar. A tonal ‘N’ logo with a Sea Salt outline appears on the sides,  with a contrasting ‘550’ branding on the lateral forefoot. Off White laces, tongue, and heel logo provide a contrasting tone to this colorway. A White chunky midsole with New Balance branding rests on a cream outsole. 

The New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede was made available on November 1st, 2022, retailing at $120.

name: Grey Indigo
title: New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo
description:
Inspired by 2000s runners, the New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo is an iteration of the New Balance 1906R  in a ‘Grey Indigo’ colorway.

The upper is made of a Natural Indigo mesh base with Castlerock leather overlays. Other upper details include the Navy Blue ‘N’ logo on the sides with a Silver outline, ‘1906’ branding on the lateral, tongue and heel branding, and a TPU heel counter. The sole unit features ABZORB and N-ergy cushioning and a Navy Blue rubber outsole with multidirectional treads for traction.

The New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo was released on August 12th, 2022, for a retail price of $155.

name: Moonbeam Natural Indigo
title: New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo
description:
The New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo reinvents the 1980s NB CT300 tennis shoe silhouette with an oversized cup outsole and side panel branding, a rubber toe wrap, and wavy lines all through the design.

  The upper of the New Balance Moonbeam Natural Indigo CT302 is moonbeam mesh with tonal overlays in suede and an indigo heel tab and the Heritage N court logo in smooth leather. Hits of team red appear on the insole and tongue, which sports exposed foam. The natural stacked ABZORB midsole matches the ProCourt-inspired leather tip wrap. The midsole is 1.7 mm higher in the heel, featuring miniature embossed branding. 

  Released on March 15, 2022, the New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo sold for $100 retail.

name: White Indigo
title: Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo
description:
The Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo features a white canvas upper with pale blue canvas Swoosh overlays and cork heel wraps. To match the moments of cork that are scattered throughout the design, a semi-translucent dubrae boasts a pattern reminiscent of it. At the heel, an embroidered flower design in a textbook illustration style. From there, a white and gum sole adds the finishing touch.

The Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo released in May of 2021 and retailed for $110.

To shop all Nike Blazer shoes, click here.

name: Indigo
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LV8 Indigo
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 07 LV8 Indigo has become a celebrated addition with a White, Obsidian-white and Black color scheme.

Built with a white leather upper, this LV8 Air Force model by Nike is highlighted by an Aqua Blue tone on the canvas that runs through the Nike Swoosh logos to the heel tab. Special details include scientific facts about the plant christened on the heel tab and a True Indigo plant embroidered on the tongue. A White midsole that rests on a Dark Cider rubber outsole completes the design.

The Nike Air Force 1 07 LV8 Indigo was made available on April 29, 2021. Initially, it retailed at $110.

name: Indigo (GS)
title: Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS)
description:
The Air Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS) is a retro-inspired grade school release of the Air Jordan 12 sneaker in a two-tone Stone Blue/Legend Blue/Obsidian colorway.

The upper is constructed with stitched Stone Blue leather highlighted by a smooth leather mudguard dressed in white. Legend Blue is used on the branded heel pull tab, inner lining, and the Jumpman logo on the outsole tip. Other details include silver metal upper eyelets, ‘TWO3’ branding running down the tongue, and ‘23’ branding at the rear on the White midsole. The sole unit comprises a carbon fiber shank and a Stone Blue herringbone outsole.

The Air Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS) was released on August 22, 2020 for a retail price of $140.

name: Indigo (Women's)
title: Nike Air Force 1 Indigo (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Indigo W is a sneaker model that comes in a combination of obsidian, white, and black color scheme.

An indigo plant that is visibly embroidered both on the left shoe of this pair at the back left, as well as on the back right of the right shoe, is where the name of this sneaker came from. The white canvas overlays all around its toebox, the light-blue-colored Nike Swoosh overlay on its sides, as well as the second light-blue-colored brand mark on its heels, are all features of this Nike Air Force 1 for women.

The Nike Air Force 1 Indigo W made its debut on the 15th of May 2021 and it had a recommended retail price of $110.

name: Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo
title: New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo
description:
The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo is crafted with a waterproof GORE-TEX fabric, and dressed in a steel grey colorway.

Designed from a mixture of suede and mesh, the sneaker uppers display a grey hue that drapes over the toe boxes, quarters, and overlays that attach to the heel and tongues. A white N logo is on both its medial and lateral sides, while "2002R" text branding resides on the heel and at the tongue, and a GORE-TEX signature logo is stitched onto the toe box. Merging all this with a densely N-ERGY cushioned midsole, the sneakers portray, finishing off its appearance.

The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo was released on August 12th, 2022, and retailed for $180.

name: Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe
title: New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe
description:
The New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe was released as part of the 2022 ‘Protection Pack' by New Balance. 

The New Balance 2002R sneakers come in an indigo mesh upper with a series of taupe suede overlays. The shoe has an unfinished aesthetic provided by the raw and tattered edges. For branding, the shoe has a white ‘N’ logo and a '2002R' logo along the side. The lightweight ABZORB midsole provides cushioning along with N-ergy technology for improved shock absorption in the heel.

The New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe was released on 26th October 2022 with its retail price set at $170.

title: Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo
description:
The Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is inspired by outdoor adventure and pays homage to the rugged terrain of the Pacific Northwest.

The Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is equipped with Nike's Air Max technology, which provides excellent cushioning and support to the wearer's feet. The outsole of the shoe is made of durable rubber, which provides excellent traction and grip on a variety of surfaces.

We think that the notable feature of the Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is its premium Natural Indigo leather upper. This form of leather is a type of vegetable-tanned leather that is produced using natural dyes extracted from indigo plants. It is known for its durability and resistance to water and other elements, making it an ideal material for outdoor shoes. The Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo was released on December 19th, 2019, and retailed at a list price of $140.

name: Indigo Haze (Women's)
title: Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze (Women's)
description:
The Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze W is an addition to Nike's Dunk lineup of sneakers in women's sizing. 

The Indigo Haze Nike Dunk Low W has a low-cut silhouette that allows for easy movement of the foot, while the padded collar and tongue offer additional cushioning and support around the ankle. Additionally, the shoe features a rubber sole that provides grip and durability, making it suitable for a wide range of activities. The toe box is perforated for added ventilation while the Nike name branding is visible on the tongue and heel tag. The Nike Swoosh is on both sides in Indigo Haze.

We especially love the Low Nike Dunk in Indigo Haze for Women for its striking colorway. The sneaker has a Sail upper with contrasting Indigo Haze overlays and Coral Chalk accents which creates a sleek and stylish look. The Nike Dunk Low Indigo Haze W was released on March 31st, 2023 at a retail price of $110.

name: White Natural Indigo Burgundy
title: New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy
description:
The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy comes in a white, natural indigo, and burgundy color scheme.

The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy has an upper constructed from leather with a deep indigo burgundy hue. The shoe features an EVA midsole for padding and comfort. The sneaker also has a cushioned tongue and collar. The shoe features a rubber outsole for grip and stability. The sneaker has a "new balance 550" lettering on the tongue and "NB'" branding on the heel. The shoe also features an "N" logo on the lateral sides and "550" lettering on one side. The shoe's midsole features "NB" and "new balance" lettering on it.

The New Balance 550 White Natural Indigo Burgundy was released at a retail price of $110 on October 19, 2022.

name: Vintage Indigo Beige
title: New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige
description:
The New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige is a retro-inspired sneaker that was released as part of the sports collection by the American brand.

This sneaker features a beige and white mesh and leather upper with hints of vintage indigo on the tongues, ankles, and branding. Other details include the trademark "N" logo on the sides, "550" labeling on the laterals, New Balance basketball branding on the tongue tag, midsole and heel, and a lace-up closing system. The design is finished with a white midsole that sits on an Indigo rubber outsole with a linear pattern.

The New Balance 550 Vintage Indigo Beige made its debut on December 14th, 2022, retailing at $110.

name: Indigo
title: Jordan 12 Retro Indigo
description:
Ever since Michael Jordan’s memorable 1997 Flu Game, the Air Jordan 12s have been a pinnacle addition to the Jordan Brand lineage. In 2020, the Air Jordan 12 Indigo brings back everything that Jordan heads love about the sneaker.

The Air Jordan 12 Indigo shares a striking resemblance to 2012’s Obsidian retro. Most Jordan 12 retros feature tumbled leather, but the Air Jordan 12 Stone Blue takes on smooth grain leather. Hits of white on the toebox and midsole add contrast to a majority Stone Blue sneaker. From there, the iconic Jumpman logo is seen on both stamped on the outsole and embroidered on the tongue. These sneakers released in August of 2020 and retailed for $190.

name: Natural Indigo
title: New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo
description: The New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo is a stylish and comfortable sneaker that is perfect for everyday wear. Made with high-quality materials, this shoe features a natural indigo colorway that is both unique and eye-catching. The upper is constructed from premium suede and mesh, while the midsole is made from lightweight REVlite foam for superior cushioning and support. The outsole is made from durable rubber, providing excellent traction and grip on any surface. This sneaker was released on September 9th, 2022, with a retail price of $150. Whether you're hitting the streets or just running errands, the New Balance 9060 Natural Indigo is a must-have addition to your sneaker collection.

name: Indigo (Women's)
title: Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (Women's)
description:
The Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (W) is part of a Nike collection that pays homage to the Indigofera Tinctoria plant, commonly referred to as True Indigo. This women's sneaker features a white upper constructed using breathable canvas with synthetic suede overlays and an embroidered Indigo plant graphic. On its upper, it has a light blue swoosh and a light blue heel tab engraved with True Indigo’s scientific information. Furthermore, it boasts a white midsole and a rubber outsole.

The women's Nike Blazer Mid 77 Indigo (W) was released on 15th June 2021. It retailed at $110.

name: Natural Indigo Suede
title: New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede
description:
The New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede is an iteration of the New Balance 550 in a Natural Indigo/Suede colorway. 

This low-top sneaker features an Indigo suede build with matching suede overlays and a White leather overlay on the ankle collar. A tonal ‘N’ logo with a Sea Salt outline appears on the sides,  with a contrasting ‘550’ branding on the lateral forefoot. Off White laces, tongue, and heel logo provide a contrasting tone to this colorway. A White chunky midsole with New Balance branding rests on a cream outsole. 

The New Balance 550 Natural Indigo Suede was made available on November 1st, 2022, retailing at $120.

name: Grey Indigo
title: New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo
description:
Inspired by 2000s runners, the New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo is an iteration of the New Balance 1906R  in a ‘Grey Indigo’ colorway.

The upper is made of a Natural Indigo mesh base with Castlerock leather overlays. Other upper details include the Navy Blue ‘N’ logo on the sides with a Silver outline, ‘1906’ branding on the lateral, tongue and heel branding, and a TPU heel counter. The sole unit features ABZORB and N-ergy cushioning and a Navy Blue rubber outsole with multidirectional treads for traction.

The New Balance 1906R Grey Indigo was released on August 12th, 2022, for a retail price of $155.

name: Moonbeam Natural Indigo
title: New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo
description:
The New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo reinvents the 1980s NB CT300 tennis shoe silhouette with an oversized cup outsole and side panel branding, a rubber toe wrap, and wavy lines all through the design.

  The upper of the New Balance Moonbeam Natural Indigo CT302 is moonbeam mesh with tonal overlays in suede and an indigo heel tab and the Heritage N court logo in smooth leather. Hits of team red appear on the insole and tongue, which sports exposed foam. The natural stacked ABZORB midsole matches the ProCourt-inspired leather tip wrap. The midsole is 1.7 mm higher in the heel, featuring miniature embossed branding. 

  Released on March 15, 2022, the New Balance CT302 Moonbeam Natural Indigo sold for $100 retail.

name: White Indigo
title: Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo
description:
The Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo features a white canvas upper with pale blue canvas Swoosh overlays and cork heel wraps. To match the moments of cork that are scattered throughout the design, a semi-translucent dubrae boasts a pattern reminiscent of it. At the heel, an embroidered flower design in a textbook illustration style. From there, a white and gum sole adds the finishing touch.

The Nike Blazer Mid 77 White Indigo released in May of 2021 and retailed for $110.

name: Indigo
title: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LV8 Indigo
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 07 LV8 Indigo has become a celebrated addition with a White, Obsidian-white and Black color scheme.

Built with a white leather upper, this LV8 Air Force model by Nike is highlighted by an Aqua Blue tone on the canvas that runs through the Nike Swoosh logos to the heel tab. Special details include scientific facts about the plant christened on the heel tab and a True Indigo plant embroidered on the tongue. A White midsole that rests on a Dark Cider rubber outsole completes the design.

The Nike Air Force 1 07 LV8 Indigo was made available on April 29, 2021. Initially, it retailed at $110.

name: Indigo (GS)
title: Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS)
description:
The Air Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS) is a retro-inspired grade school release of the Air Jordan 12 sneaker in a two-tone Stone Blue/Legend Blue/Obsidian colorway.

The upper is constructed with stitched Stone Blue leather highlighted by a smooth leather mudguard dressed in white. Legend Blue is used on the branded heel pull tab, inner lining, and the Jumpman logo on the outsole tip. Other details include silver metal upper eyelets, ‘TWO3’ branding running down the tongue, and ‘23’ branding at the rear on the White midsole. The sole unit comprises a carbon fiber shank and a Stone Blue herringbone outsole.

The Air Jordan 12 Retro Indigo (GS) was released on August 22, 2020 for a retail price of $140.

name: Indigo (Women's)
title: Nike Air Force 1 Indigo (Women's)
description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Indigo W is a sneaker model that comes in a combination of obsidian, white, and black color scheme.

An indigo plant that is visibly embroidered both on the left shoe of this pair at the back left, as well as on the back right of the right shoe, is where the name of this sneaker came from. The white canvas overlays all around its toebox, the light-blue-colored Nike Swoosh overlay on its sides, as well as the second light-blue-colored brand mark on its heels, are all features of this Nike Air Force 1 for women.

The Nike Air Force 1 Indigo W made its debut on the 15th of May 2021 and it had a recommended retail price of $110.

name: Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo
title: New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo
description:
The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo is crafted with a waterproof GORE-TEX fabric, and dressed in a steel grey colorway.

Designed from a mixture of suede and mesh, the sneaker uppers display a grey hue that drapes over the toe boxes, quarters, and overlays that attach to the heel and tongues. A white N logo is on both its medial and lateral sides, while "2002R" text branding resides on the heel and at the tongue, and a GORE-TEX signature logo is stitched onto the toe box. Merging all this with a densely N-ERGY cushioned midsole, the sneakers portray, finishing off its appearance.

The New Balance 2002R Gore-Tex Magnet Mood Indigo was released on August 12th, 2022, and retailed for $180.

name: Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe
title: New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe
description:
The New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe was released as part of the 2022 ‘Protection Pack' by New Balance. 

The New Balance 2002R sneakers come in an indigo mesh upper with a series of taupe suede overlays. The shoe has an unfinished aesthetic provided by the raw and tattered edges. For branding, the shoe has a white ‘N’ logo and a '2002R' logo along the side. The lightweight ABZORB midsole provides cushioning along with N-ergy technology for improved shock absorption in the heel.

The New Balance 2002R Vintage Indigo Calm Taupe was released on 26th October 2022 with its retail price set at $170.

description:
The Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is inspired by outdoor adventure and pays homage to the rugged terrain of the Pacific Northwest.

The Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is equipped with Nike's Air Max technology, which provides excellent cushioning and support to the wearer's feet. The outsole of the shoe is made of durable rubber, which provides excellent traction and grip on a variety of surfaces.

We think that the notable feature of the Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo is its premium Natural Indigo leather upper. This form of leather is a type of vegetable-tanned leather that is produced using natural dyes extracted from indigo plants. It is known for its durability and resistance to water and other elements, making it an ideal material for outdoor shoes. The Nike Air Max 90 Lahar Escape Natural Indigo was released on December 19th, 2019, and retailed at a list price of $140.
